{"tid":2083244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"表態?","createTime":"2020-06-28T15:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T15:36:18.000Z","uid":339906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"479621c30c2cb06d8ca3cf8daa37da6099fa24d2","tid":2083244,"uid":339906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"不少政界中人紛紛以各種形式「表態」。例如，民主派元老李柱銘日早接受外媒訪問，強調不認為「攬炒」。上周五，前政務司司長陳方安生日前以年屆80，女兒離世，需時復原及想「過較平靜生活」為由，宣布引退；鼓吹「城邦論」的陳雲今日亦貼文宣布退出香港社會，更趁機批評「泛民港獨將香港推入國際政治鬥爭的黑洞」。<br />\n<br />\n政界中人認為，政界人中近期的各式表態可謂一種「儀式」，即是趁「港區國安法」生效前，為自己過去所做的劃上一個句號，以免不可預期的「秋後算帳」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2681511/%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E9%A7%92%E6%A3%84%E4%BF%9D%E6%BD%9B%E9%80%83%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E3%80%80%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E7%B4%9B%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E6%8B%92%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2681511%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A7%2592%25E6%25A3%2584%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%25BD%259B%25E9%2580%2583%25E8%258D%25B7%25E8%2598%25AD%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B4%259B%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=53f6a08e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2681511/%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E9%A7%92%E6%A3%84%E4%BF%9D%E6%BD%9B%E9%80%83%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E3%80%80%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E7%B4%9B%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E6%8B%92%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8</a>"},{"pid":"3911de1282e18bf0dd1ec0d2404fc5e07fdda31f","tid":2083244,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pBnePd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pBnePd.gif&h=d1d0a7c4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}